      {
        "label": "\n        1. The Essentialist\n      ",
        "href": "text/part0004.html",
        "subitems": []
      },
      {
        "label": "\n        Part I: Essence: What is the core mind-set of an Essentialist?\n      ",
        "href": "text/part0005.html",
        "subitems": [
          {
            "label": "\n          2. Choose: The Invincible Power of Choice\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0007.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          3. Discern: The Unimportance of Practically Everything\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0008.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          4. Trade-Off: Which Problem Do I Want?\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0009.html",
            "subitems": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "label": "\n        Part II: Explore: How can we discern the trivial many from the vital few?\n      ",
        "href": "text/part0010.html",
        "subitems": [
          {
            "label": "\n          5. Escape: The Perks of Being Unavailable\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0012.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          6. Look: See What Really Matters\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0013.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          7. Play: Embrace the Wisdom of Your Inner Child\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0014.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          8. Sleep: Protect the Asset\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0015.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          9. Select: The Power of Extreme Criteria\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0016.html",
            "subitems": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "label": "\n        Part III: Eliminate: How can we cut out the trivial many?\n      ",
        "href": "text/part0017.html",
        "subitems": [
          {
            "label": "\n          10. Clarify: One Decision That Makes a Thousand\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0019.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          11. Dare: The Power of a Graceful “No”\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0020.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          12. Uncommit: Win Big by Cutting Your Losses\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0021.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          13. Edit: The Invisible Art\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0022.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          14. Limit: The Freedom of Setting Boundaries\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0023.html",
            "subitems": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "label": "\n        Part IV: Execute: How can we make doing the vital few things almost effortless?\n      ",
        "href": "text/part0024.html",
        "subitems": [
          {
            "label": "\n          15. Buffer: The Unfair Advantage\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0026.html",
            "subitems": []
          },
          {
            "label": "\n          16. Subtract: Bring Forth More by Removing Obstacles\n        ",
            "href": "text/part0027.html",
            "subitems": []
